data.name: RealTargetRatio.CommandText
data.value:
select * from(
select isnull(c2.[Year],c1.[Year]) as [Year], isnull(c2.[Department],c1.[Department]) as Department, isnull(Sum(c2.Real),0) as RealSum, c1.QuarterTarget, isnull(round((Sum(c2.Real)/c1.QuarterTarget*100),1),0) as RealTargetRatio from (select * from Competition2 where [Date] <= convert(char(10), getdate(), 120) and Year='2022' and Month in('7','8','9') ) c2 full join ((select distinct [Year],Department,QuarterTarget from Competition1 where Department not in ('媒體部','顧問室','資訊部','中高階獵才部') and Year='2022' and Month in('7','8','9'))) c1 on c1.[Year]=c2.[Year] and c1.Department=c2.Department group by isnull(c2.[Year],c1.[Year]),isnull(c2.[Department],c1.[Department]),c1.QuarterTarget
union
select distinct c1.[Year] ,c1.[Department] ,isnull((SELECT SUM(sd.CustAmt) FROM ERPSalesMaster sm left join ERPSalesDetails sd on sm.[SalesMasterNO]=sd.[SalesMasterNO] WHERE sm.IsActive=1 and sd.IsActive=1 and sm.SalesTypeID IN ('1','31') AND sd.SalesDate between'2022-07-01' and '2022-09-30' and sd.SalesDate<= GETDATE()),0) as RealSum ,c1.QuarterTarget ,isnull(round(((SELECT SUM(sd.CustAmt) FROM ERPSalesMaster sm left join ERPSalesDetails sd on sm.[SalesMasterNO]=sd.[SalesMasterNO] WHERE sm.IsActive=1 and sd.IsActive=1 and sm.SalesTypeID IN ('1','31') AND sd.SalesDate between'2022-07-01' and '2022-09-30' and sd.SalesDate<= GETDATE())/c1.QuarterTarget*100),1),0) as RealTargetRatio from Competition1 c1 where c1.Department = '媒體部' and c1.[Year]='2022' and c1.[Month] in('7','8','9')
union
select distinct c1.[Year] ,c1.[Department] ,isnull((SELECT SUM(sd.Amount) FROM JBERP.dbo.SalesMaster sm left join JBERP.dbo.SalesDetails sd on sm.SalesNO=sd.SalesNO WHERE sm.IsActive=1 and sm.SalesTypeID IN ('12','18','13') AND sm.SalesDate between'2022-07-01' and '2022-09-30' and sm.SalesDate<= GETDATE()),0) as RealSum ,c1.QuarterTarget ,isnull(round(((SELECT SUM(sd.Amount) FROM JBERP.dbo.SalesMaster sm left join JBERP.dbo.SalesDetails sd on sm.SalesNO=sd.SalesNO WHERE sm.IsActive=1 and sm.SalesTypeID IN ('12','18','13') AND sm.SalesDate between'2022-07-01' and '2022-09-30' and sm.SalesDate<= GETDATE())/c1.QuarterTarget*100),1),0) as RealTargetRatio from Competition1 c1 where c1.Department = '顧問室' and c1.[Year]='2022' and c1.[Month] in('7','8','9')
union
select distinct c1.[Year] ,c1.[Department] ,isnull((SELECT SUM(sd.Amount) FROM JBERP.dbo.SalesMaster sm left join JBERP.dbo.SalesDetails sd on sm.SalesNO=sd.SalesNO WHERE sm.IsActive=1 and sm.SalesTypeID IN ('4','4A') AND sm.SalesDate between'2022-07-01' and '2022-09-30' and sm.SalesDate<= GETDATE()),0) as RealSum ,c1.QuarterTarget ,isnull(round(((SELECT SUM(sd.Amount) FROM JBERP.dbo.SalesMaster sm left join JBERP.dbo.SalesDetails sd on sm.SalesNO=sd.SalesNO WHERE sm.IsActive=1 and sm.SalesTypeID IN ('4','4A') AND sm.SalesDate between'2022-07-01' and '2022-09-30' and sm.SalesDate<= GETDATE())/c1.QuarterTarget*100),1),0) as RealTargetRatio from Competition1 c1 where c1.Department = '資訊部' and c1.[Year]='2022' and c1.[Month] in('7','8','9')
union
select distinct c1.[Year] ,c1.[Department] ,isnull((SELECT SUM(sd.Amount) FROM JBERP.dbo.SalesMaster sm left join JBERP.dbo.SalesDetails sd on sm.SalesNO=sd.SalesNO WHERE sm.IsActive=1 and sm.SalesTypeID IN ('30') and sm.SalesID in('010','204','278','412','427') AND sm.SalesDate between'2022-07-01' and '2022-09-30' and sm.SalesDate<= GETDATE()),0) as RealSum ,c1.QuarterTarget ,isnull(round(((SELECT SUM(sd.Amount) FROM JBERP.dbo.SalesMaster sm left join JBERP.dbo.SalesDetails sd on sm.SalesNO=sd.SalesNO WHERE sm.IsActive=1 and sm.SalesTypeID IN ('30') and sm.SalesID in('010','204','278','412','427') AND sm.SalesDate between'2022-07-01' and '2022-09-30' and sm.SalesDate<= GETDATE())/c1.QuarterTarget*100),1),0) as RealTargetRatio
from Competition1 c1 where c1.Department = '中高階獵才部' and c1.[Year]='2022' and c1.[Month] in('7','8','9')
) ttt order by( CASE Department WHEN '人才服務台北' THEN '0' WHEN '外勞事業部' THEN '1' WHEN'人才服務桃園' THEN '2' WHEN '傑誠國際村' THEN '3' WHEN '媒體部' THEN '4' WHEN '人才服務新竹' THEN '5' WHEN '資訊部' THEN '6' WHEN '中高階獵才部' THEN '7' WHEN '顧問室' THEN '8' ELSE '9' END) asc

data.name: AccumRealTargetRatio1.CommandText
data.value: select t1.[Year],t1.[Month],t1.Department,t1.RealSum,t1.QuarterTarget,isnull((sum(t2.RealSum)/t1.QuarterTarget*100),0) as AccumRatio from ( select isnull(c2.[Year],c1.[Year]) as [Year],isnull(c2.[Month],4) as [Month],isnull(c2.[Department],c1.[Department]) as Department,isnull(Sum(c2.Real),0) as RealSum,c1.QuarterTarget,isnull((Sum(c2.Real)/c1.QuarterTarget),0) as RealTargetRatio from Competition2 c2 full join (select distinct Year,Department,QuarterTarget from Competition1) c1 on c1.[Year]=c2.[Year] and c1.Department=c2.Department group by c2.[Year],c1.[Year],c2.[Month],c2.[Department],c1.[Department],c1.QuarterTarget )t1 inner join ( select isnull(c2.[Year],c1.[Year]) as [Year],isnull(c2.[Month],4) as [Month],isnull(c2.[Department],c1.[Department]) as Department,isnull(Sum(c2.Real),0) as RealSum,c1.QuarterTarget,isnull((Sum(c2.Real)/c1.QuarterTarget),0) as RealTargetRatio from Competition2 c2 full join (select distinct Year,Department,QuarterTarget from Competition1) c1 on c1.[Year]=c2.[Year] and c1.Department=c2.Department group by c2.[Year],c1.[Year],c2.[Month],c2.[Department],c1.[Department],c1.QuarterTarget )t2 on t1.[Month] >= t2.[Month] and t1.[Year] = t2.[Year] and t1.[Department] = t2.[Department] group by t1.[Year],t1.[Month],t1.Department,t1.RealSum,t1.QuarterTarget

data.name: AccumRealTargetRatio.CommandText
data.value:
select convert(varchar,Month(t1.[Date]))+'/'+convert(varchar,Day(t1.[Date])) as [Date1],t1.[Date],t1.Department,t1.[Real],t1.QuarterTarget,isnull(round((sum(t2.Real)/t1.QuarterTarget*100),1),0) as AccumRatio,sum(t2.Real) as sigma from ( select c2.[Date],c2.[Department] ,c2.Real,c1.QuarterTarget from Competition2 c2 left join (select distinct [Year],Department,QuarterTarget from Competition1 where Year='2022' and Month in('7','8','9')) c1 on c1.[Year]=c2.[Year] and c1.Department=c2.Department where c2.Department not in ('媒體部','顧問室','資訊部','中高階獵才部') and c2.[Year]='2022' and c2.[Month] in('7','8','9')
union
select c2.[Date],c2.[Department] ,c2.Real,c1.QuarterTarget from (
SELECT Year(sd.SalesDate) as [Year] ,sd.SalesDate as [Date] ,'媒體部' as Department ,sum(sd.CustAmt) as [Real] FROM ERPSalesMaster sm left join ERPSalesDetails sd on sm.[SalesMasterNO]=sd.[SalesMasterNO] WHERE sm.IsActive=1 and sd.IsActive=1 and sm.SalesTypeID IN ('1','31') AND sd.SalesDate between'2022-07-01' and '2022-09-30' group by sd.SalesDate
union
SELECT Year(sm.SalesDate) as [Year], left(convert(varchar,sm.SalesDate,120),10) as [Date], '顧問室' as Department, sum(sd.Amount) as [Real] FROM JBERP.dbo.SalesMaster sm left join JBERP.dbo.SalesDetails sd on sm.SalesNO=sd.SalesNO where sm.IsActive=1 and sm.SalesTypeID IN ('12','18','13') AND (sm.SalesDate between'2022-07-01' and '2022-09-30') group by SalesDate
union
SELECT Year(sm.SalesDate) as [Year], left(convert(varchar,sm.SalesDate,120),10) as [Date], '資訊部' as Department, sum(sd.Amount) as [Real] FROM JBERP.dbo.SalesMaster sm left join JBERP.dbo.SalesDetails sd on sm.SalesNO=sd.SalesNO where sm.IsActive=1 and sm.SalesTypeID IN ('4','4A') AND (sm.SalesDate between'2022-07-01' and '2022-09-30') group by SalesDate
union
SELECT Year(sm.SalesDate) as [Year], left(convert(varchar,sm.SalesDate,120),10) as [Date], '中高階獵才部' as Department, sum(sd.Amount) as [Real] FROM JBERP.dbo.SalesMaster sm left join JBERP.dbo.SalesDetails sd on sm.SalesNO=sd.SalesNO where sm.IsActive=1 and sm.SalesTypeID IN ('30') AND (sm.SalesDate between'2022-07-01' and '2022-09-30') and sm.SalesID in('010','204','278','412','427') group by SalesDate
) c2 left join (select distinct [Year],Department,QuarterTarget from Competition1 where Year='2022' and Month in('7','8','9')) c1 on c1.[Year]=c2.[Year] and c1.Department=c2.Department
)t1
inner join (
select c2.[Date],c2.[Department] ,c2.Real,c1.QuarterTarget from Competition2 c2 left join (select distinct [Year],Department,QuarterTarget from Competition1 where Year='2022' and Month in('7','8','9')) c1 on c1.[Year]=c2.[Year] and c1.Department=c2.Department where c2.Department not in ('媒體部','顧問室','資訊部','中高階獵才部') and c2.[Year]='2022' and c2.[Month] in('7','8','9')
union
select c2.[Date],c2.[Department] ,c2.Real,c1.QuarterTarget from (
SELECT Year(sd.SalesDate) as [Year] ,sd.SalesDate as [Date] ,'媒體部' as Department ,sum(sd.CustAmt) as [Real] FROM ERPSalesMaster sm left join ERPSalesDetails sd on sm.[SalesMasterNO]=sd.[SalesMasterNO] WHERE sm.IsActive=1 and sd.IsActive=1 and sm.SalesTypeID IN ('1','31') AND sd.SalesDate between'2022-07-01' and '2022-09-30' group by sd.SalesDate
union
SELECT Year(sm.SalesDate) as [Year], left(convert(varchar,sm.SalesDate,120),10) as [Date], '顧問室' as Department, sum(sd.Amount) as [Real] FROM JBERP.dbo.SalesMaster sm left join JBERP.dbo.SalesDetails sd on sm.SalesNO=sd.SalesNO where sm.IsActive=1 and sm.SalesTypeID IN ('12','18','13') AND (sm.SalesDate between'2022-07-01' and '2022-09-30') group by SalesDate
union
SELECT Year(sm.SalesDate) as [Year], left(convert(varchar,sm.SalesDate,120),10) as [Date], '資訊部' as Department, sum(sd.Amount) as [Real] FROM JBERP.dbo.SalesMaster sm left join JBERP.dbo.SalesDetails sd on sm.SalesNO=sd.SalesNO where sm.IsActive=1 and sm.SalesTypeID IN ('4','4A') AND (sm.SalesDate between'2022-07-01' and '2022-09-30') group by SalesDate
union
SELECT Year(sm.SalesDate) as [Year], left(convert(varchar,sm.SalesDate,120),10) as [Date], '中高階獵才部' as Department, sum(sd.Amount) as [Real] FROM JBERP.dbo.SalesMaster sm left join JBERP.dbo.SalesDetails sd on sm.SalesNO=sd.SalesNO where sm.IsActive=1 and sm.SalesTypeID IN ('30') AND (sm.SalesDate between'2022-07-01' and '2022-09-30') and sm.SalesID in('010','204','278','412','427') group by SalesDate
) c2 left join (select distinct [Year],Department,QuarterTarget from Competition1 where Year='2022' and Month in('7','8','9')) c1 on c1.[Year]=c2.[Year] and c1.Department=c2.Department
)t2 on t1.[Date] >= t2.[Date] and t1.[Department] = t2.[Department]
where t1.Real !=0 and t1.[Date] <= convert(char(10), getdate(), 120) group by t1.[Date],t1.Department,t1.[Real],t1.QuarterTarget order by Date

data.name: AccumRealTargetRatio2.CommandText
data.value: select t1.[Date],t1.Department,t1.[Real],t1.QuarterTarget,isnull((sum(t2.Real)/t1.QuarterTarget*100),0) as AccumRatio from ( select c2.[Date],c2.[Department] ,c2.Real,c1.QuarterTarget from Competition2 c2 left join (select distinct [Year],Department,QuarterTarget from Competition1) c1 on c1.[Year]=c2.[Year] and c1.Department=c2.Department )t1 inner join ( select c2.[Date],c2.[Department] ,c2.Real,c1.QuarterTarget from Competition2 c2 left join (select distinct [Year],Department,QuarterTarget from Competition1) c1 on c1.[Year]=c2.[Year] and c1.Department=c2.Department )t2 on t1.[Date] >= t2.[Date] and t1.[Department] = t2.[Department] group by t1.[Date],t1.Department,t1.[Real],t1.QuarterTarget

data.name: RealTargetRatio1.CommandText
data.value: select isnull(c2.[Year],c1.[Year]) as [Year],isnull(c2.[Department],c1.[Department]) as Department,isnull(Sum(c2.Real),0) as RealSum,c1.QuarterTarget,isnull((Sum(c2.Real)/c1.QuarterTarget*100),0) as RealTargetRatio from Competition2 c2 full join ((select distinct Year,Department,QuarterTarget from Competition1)) c1 on c1.[Year]=c2.[Year] and c1.Department=c2.Department group by isnull(c2.[Year],c1.[Year]),isnull(c2.[Department],c1.[Department]),c1.QuarterTarget
